wiki.summary: “You & Me” is the second solo single by South Korean singer JENNIE. It tells a fiery tale of unwavering love, accompanied by a vibrant dance-pop rhythm and a bouncy bassline. The captivating song made its debut on stage during JENNIE’s solo performance as part of BLACKPINK’s BORN PINK WORLD TOUR on October 15, 2022. Following the tour’s grand finale on September 17th, 2023, the highly anticipated track was released on October 6, 2023, as a special gift to fans. Read more on Last.fm.
